      <title outputclass="H3_1_9" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">3.603</ph> Responsibilities of the contracting officer.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d129e13">
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d131e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  Before awarding a contract, the contracting officer shall obtain an authorization under <xref href="FAR-i1124277.dita#i1124277"
                        base="i1124277"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">3.602</xref> if-</p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d129e26">
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d131e30" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        The contracting officer knows, or has reason to believe, that a prospective contractor is one to which award is otherwise prohibited under <xref href="FAR-i1124266.dita#i1124266"
                              base="i1124266"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">3.601</xref>; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d131e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        There is a most compelling reason to make an award to that prospective contractor.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d131e53" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
